gm gm - I'm assuming it makes no difference how many LP positions I have open/active at one time? will SN10 rewards be distributed the same whether I have one $1000 position active vs two $500 positions active? (with different price ranges)
Correct
No difference

your positions are very small and are in a very wide range, so the portion of daily emissions you receive will be relatively small. 
The reason you don't get rewards on a daily basis is because the portion you receive is so small that it often doesn't meet the minimum threshold of alpha that needs to be transferred (iirc it's roughly 0.002 TAO worth of SN10 tokens). We do account for this and add up small rewards over time and send it once it passes the minimum transfer threshold though. 
if you want more SN10 rewards you should deposit more liquidity and/or place them in a much tigher price range.

Congrats to the team for this first stress test on the pool !! 
Great success
